{"tid":342951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：(林鄭)呢個馬步，勾起陳雲美好的舊區回憶。","createTime":"2017-08-01T04:59:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-01T04:59:45.000Z","uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eadbbc1e273cecf4cf5ccc954c8f0757ea205848","tid":342951,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T04:59:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/01/125902_3a933d0e3874ca36ed7a3861e68437ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F01%2F125902_3a933d0e3874ca36ed7a3861e68437ed.jpg&h=c8fb7caf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳雲：紮行個馬。即管放馬過來。呢個馬步，勾起陳雲美好的舊區回憶。我講個古仔比大家聽。<br />\n話說一九八七年，我在深水埗能仁書院教夜校，經過北河街露天小販市集。一男一女小販在爭位，跟住罵戰，引來圍觀。雙方爭持不下。最後，罵戰如此結束。<br />\n男：我屌你吖嗱，你擺檔咁撚霸道，街坊街里大家都見到你無道理，你係咪想摟屌先？<br />\n女：講得出做得到，你係咪屌先?<br />\n跟住個女小販撩起裙裾，紮起個馬，等個男小販過來。<br />\n男：你玩到咁盡...我邊夠你玩。搵食者，呢個位比你。<br />\n件事寫了在懷舊散文集《新不如舊》，用複述方式。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10155476510627225&amp;set=a.469456247224.249505.589657224&amp;type=3&amp;permPage=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10155476510627225%26set%3Da.469456247224.249505.589657224%26type%3D3%26permPage%3D1&d=mVlYyMYxp8RAGMAxak8MbP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=20793a8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10155476510627225&amp;set=a.469456247224.249505.589657224&amp;type=3&amp;permPage=1</a>"}]}